 dissect a C.E.O.=E2=80=99s crisis management tactics and humiliate him wit=
h questions about financial calculations=E2=80=94such as Rapino=E2=80=99s q=
uestion, after the second day of the festival was canceled, =E2=80=9CHow mu=
ch does Travis owe us do we have advance?=E2=80=9D=E2=80=94could undermine =
that pro-business agenda.

