In Disney=E2=80=99s eyes, however, Garnett drew a faulty distinction betwee=
n an effort to control the message or content of The Mandalorian=E2=80=94wh=
ich would be illegitimate under the First Amendment=E2=80=94and a permissib=
le challenge over retaliation for off-the-job political speech. Disney sees=
